title: Update: Woman dies in motorcycle crash in Henderson (New Zealand Police)
text: ( Source : New Zealand Police ) Waitemata Police can confirm that a 52-year-old woman has died after a motorcycle crash in Henderson this afternoon. The woman, who was a pillion passanger on the motorbike, was transported to Auckland hospital
